{"h7e72b50dgcdb7g49ffgb262gc3f6bd223edf": ["I hardly need a bodyguard, Tilses. This isn't Avernus.", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingLeader_AD_WithGuard.html", "39925ef0-6c98-eb6f-e0c4-78a431157eed"], "h7b998ae3gf158g4517g98c0gc52c41bf3fda": ["No sir. At least the monsters there <i>looked </i>like monsters.", "3ff71f38-28e9-4e72-ba17-9f6d3bb2a995", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingLeader_AD_WithGuard.html", "45ea48ed-79e9-9a78-24cd-2df26ce7c4a2"], "h71969e93g9710g4604gbe69g7646633c1d54": ["The Watch or the Flaming Fist?", "3ff71f38-28e9-4e72-ba17-9f6d3bb2a995", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingLeader_AD_WithGuard.html", "9b48e02b-5d21-3878-4fc7-1f6b243ebb1a"], "hd137527dgb0deg4ff1g86f2g6cf6b1bd2b11": ["Pardon?", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingLeader_AD_WithGuard.html", "cb94325e-6c91-a6a6-5f06-01f8488d5a6b"], "hce9606deg401bg45d5g9b78g72fbb6878a0b": ["When we get to Baldur's Gate. Where are we enlisting?", "3ff71f38-28e9-4e72-ba17-9f6d3bb2a995", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingLeader_AD_WithGuard.html", "b31d47f4-9f83-6d11-8040-6cf15ae07382"], "h4339eaf7g47f1g4606g8f8agdf3892628201": ["I'm done soldiering, Tilly. I'd like a clean start.", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingLeader_AD_WithGuard.html", "f76646c8-3aec-e93f-293d-513eadbad201"], "hc09b11c7g7cccg43c8gbaabg094de72e2d4d": ["But go with the Watch. You're too honest to be a mercenary.", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingLeader_AD_WithGuard.html", "3b9cd0af-3d00-bd17-7fde-456745961a43"], "hbe9f9d50g01c6g4375g886ag69cbfb2add12": ["Commander -", "3ff71f38-28e9-4e72-ba17-9f6d3bb2a995", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingLeader_AD_WithGuard.html", "e491d8e2-5ecb-4d93-ad08-abbb833f011e"], "h6379efccg6e01g48dfga4ebg351aa9fc7555": ["Just Zevlor, Tilly. We're civilians now, remember?", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingLeader_AD_WithGuard.html", "29133727-e7de-b535-a280-124f75dac7db"], "h607843afg246dg451cgb8cbgffdd86475403": ["With respect, sir - being a Hellrider is for life. They can't take -", "3ff71f38-28e9-4e72-ba17-9f6d3bb2a995", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingLeader_AD_WithGuard.html", "2c46f7d6-e50d-f8a9-d823-401eb8bfdbc3"], "h0d2e0736g0941g4b79gb50agc64d4962ac74": ["They can, and did. Avernus changed things - best we get used to that.", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingLeader_AD_WithGuard.html", "6ffcaea7-5bb2-7471-b58c-2fd23bb376b5"], "hbccb36fbgfff3g4dd4gb0d2gfec892ce1055": ["... yes, Zevlor.", "3ff71f38-28e9-4e72-ba17-9f6d3bb2a995", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingLeader_AD_WithGuard.html", "ee8174c3-45ba-a556-6769-97a29a50c1ec"], "hc92030cdg30b7g4047g9bfbg618c28978924": ["No word from the scouts yet?", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingLeader_AD_WithGuard.html", "bfead7fb-5b9a-19a5-07d3-b2625ea79968"], "h0745357fg1313g4cfbg87b9gcb6568d13441": ["No sir. But if there's a clear path past those goblins, they'll find it.", "3ff71f38-28e9-4e72-ba17-9f6d3bb2a995", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingLeader_AD_WithGuard.html", "772c7c43-97a8-f6bd-b5ff-63a316721c49"], "hf6f217bcgcac9g4378gbabfgdb9825c46d45": ["Yes. Of course.", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_TieflingLeader_AD_WithGuard.html", "9c1c240e-1c9e-50c5-ec4a-2604ff4a6119"]}